664
00:52:34,040 --> 00:52:38,210


665
00:52:38,210 --> 00:52:42,220


666
00:52:43,280 --> 00:52:47,360


667
00:52:47,420 --> 00:52:51,690


668
00:52:52,350 --> 00:52:56,500


669
00:52:56,590 --> 00:53:00,240


670
00:53:01,530 --> 00:53:05,840


671
00:53:07,170 --> 00:53:11,550


672
00:53:45,640 --> 00:53:47,500
Ďakujem.

673
00:53:47,680 --> 00:53:49,360
Nemáš zač.

674
00:53:55,550 --> 00:53:56,600
Kto je to?

675
00:53:59,050 --> 00:54:00,500
Niekto, koho chcem očariť.

676
00:54:04,290 --> 00:54:06,620
To rada počujem.

677
00:54:08,860 --> 00:54:10,080
Ako sa môže stať človek dobrým človekom?

678
00:54:11,470 --> 00:54:13,080
Aký je to dobrý človek?

679
00:54:14,940 --> 00:54:16,280
Je to človek plný lásky.

